Follow the below steps to run this example:

Linux
	* First you must be logged in a Linux machine with the root user
	* Second, in the command line go to the 'RegistryServiceAtBoot' directory and type './gradlew'

Windows
	* This example does not run on Windows because we are adding a Linux only service
	* It was created to show you how you can conditionally use the Module.hook to not install the entire module in some environments
